latestPosts.caption:
Denim, but make it couture.
A structured denim corset meets the grace of a chanderi draped skirt, all elevated with hand-done denim patching and aqua-toned motifs — creating the ultimate east-meets-west vibe.

Styled on the fierce @sshorwala, this silhouette is all things easy, breezy, and head-turning. Whether it’s a destination wedding brunch or a dreamy coastal dinner, this look speaks confidence, creativity, and couture craftsmanship.

For the muse who blends bold with beautiful — and wears every layer like a story. 💙🌊
